flowchart TB
  Start[AppSec trigger] --> Classify[Classifier]
  Classify --> Init[Evidence dirs]
  Init --> Scan[Scans and review]
  Scan --> Findings[Normalize findings]
  Findings --> Threat[Threat model]
  Threat --> DAST[Passive DAST baseline]
  DAST --> Need{Need active pentest?}
  Need -->|yes| ROE[Recommend ROE, never auto-run]
  Need -->|no| Validate[Evidence validator]
  ROE --> Validate
  Validate --> Gate[appsec gate.check]
